  "title": "Leasing Manager (Full-Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>SMTP Consult Pte Ltd is a family office concierge service firm that caters to our client’s needs as they immigrate to Singapore. Our goal is to help our clients with their relocation needs as they settle in Singapore and provide bespoke services based on their specific requirements.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking a dynamic Leasing Manager to drive occupancy growth and deepen client relationships within a fast-paced co-working environment, leveraging strategic sales leadership and community-building expertise.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and implement data-driven sales strategies to exceed occupancy and revenue goals in a competitive co-working market</li><li>Generate qualified leads through proactive networking, cold outreach, LinkedIn engagement, and cultivating referral partnerships</li><li>Conduct engaging space tours and deliver tailored presentations that effectively communicate amenities and community value</li><li>Provide exceptional, personalised service to onboard new members smoothly and foster long-term client loyalty</li><li>Analyse sales metrics and market intelligence to continuously refine sales approaches and strengthen competitive positioning</li><li>Maintain regular client communication, gather actionable feedback, and lead process improvements to enhance satisfaction and retention</li><li>Lead, coach, and motivate the sales team by delivering on-the-job training, developing skills, and tracking performance using KPIs, such as conversion rates and space utilisation</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree or higher in any discipline</li><li>Proven self-motivation with a hunter mentality and demonstrated ability to build and maintain strong client relationships</li><li>Established network of relationships with co-working brokers and commercial real estate agencies</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>EA License Name & License Number: SMTP Consult Pte. Ltd. (23C1754)</li><li>EA Personnel Name & Registration Number: Keith Wong (R24125987)</li></ul>",
